{"tid":1047919,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"康健中心2.8億合約疑益自己友 陳肇始辯稱「唔記得」榮譽贊助人身份","createTime":"2019-03-05T09:38:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-11T14:23:06.000Z","uid":150685,"like":3,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7574691f45fd804d12268d00546b4cc6aaa0dc00","tid":1047919,"uid":150685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T09:38:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190305/large/1551751647_0466.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190305%2Flarge%2F1551751647_0466.png&h=84ea51e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n政府首個地區康健中心由葵青區議會副主席兼政協周奕希擔任主席的「葵青安全社區及健康城市協會」奪得運營權，3年營運合約達2.8億元。食物及衞生局局長陳肇始被揭發是該協會的榮譽贊助人，外界質疑涉利益輸送。陳肇始今早澄清自己並無參與中心招標遴選，連有哪些機構投標都不知道，她稱在不少組織都有類似榮譽身份，對於自己是該協會的榮譽贊助人，「坦白講都唔記得咗」，但日後會重新檢視這些職位是否需要避嫌。<br />\n<br />\n陳重申，過去雖然有參與「葵青安全社區及健康城市協會」舉辦的活動，但並無參與實際會務，亦無作出捐款，整體上並不存在利益衝突，但為了釋除公眾疑慮，她已決定盡快去信協會辭任榮譽贊助人。<br />\n<br />\n她強調，地區康健中心設有中央投標委員會負責為遴選把關，自己並無參與遴選，又透露評選時，機構的服務質素評分佔70%，其餘30%則是價錢因素。<br />\n<br />\n最新一份《財政預算案》已為康健中心預留1.5億元作營運費用，陳指已要求營運者在今年10月1日前要投入運作，康健中心會以預防為本，主要是為增加市民的健康知識，亦會提供簡單身體檢查，若發現求診者有健康問題就會轉介私家醫生跟進。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190305/59331226\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190305%2F59331226&d=aJy3RA7fpCa2KE6CQkcak7XxB%2B4AiQz8bo105MOPl14%3D&h=777313c1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190305%2F59331226&h=b406ee49\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190305/59331226</a>"},{"pid":"6b77c921eaf3171a510d458ec22e5bb643529b7a","tid":1047919,"uid":124410,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T13:27:51.000Z","msg":"屌<br />\n仆街派明利益衝突啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92a9134bb69fc0f6a7814383e41475c45db17600","tid":1047919,"uid":40250,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T13:59:29.000Z","msg":"咁老實講，佢又無份選，好難話關佢事"},{"pid":"72af33dcebca06fdcc05347d48b843b2cd53aaf8","tid":1047919,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T14:57:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50b5bb8e9963e93e24c20dd6988e6955c3ef57c6","tid":1047919,"uid":19725,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T15:27:40.000Z","msg":"屌佢 臭護士"},{"pid":"32136face1a53cbb53a20b2619c9cbb207166c52","tid":1047919,"uid":176166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T15:32:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cd2f26a2173fd0419456aeacc8c4cd4e278d8b0c","tid":1047919,"uid":63287,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T15:49:02.000Z","msg":"垃圾中心一個燒銀紙。<br />\n<br />\n邊有人得閒上去😨<br />\n<br />\n搵d 流動車去屋村樓下做下量血壓講座唔好？"},{"pid":"a6c4b1f782a0702005d84658f2ad39fb0d81ee32","tid":1047919,"uid":124410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T00:24:37.000Z","msg":"利益輸送<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c321052a1d155b88a2158b4a7083ceae7ebdb33c","tid":1047919,"uid":176166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T14:03:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"85b5f1071cab217ff20ccbb37ec90e2871f9526b","tid":1047919,"uid":176166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T14:23:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}